data.description: Military relocation - priced to sell with $5,000 in additional cash toward closing available with reasonable offer! Captivating cul-de-sac living in historic St. Augustine! Indulge in the expansive layout of this home, where the open concept living space artfully divides distinct areas for a harmonious living experience. The master suite is a secluded retreat in its own wing, featuring two spacious closets and a generously proportioned bathroom. Two additional bedrooms are thoughtfully situated with a conveniently placed bathroom that also caters to guests' comfort.  Adding to the allure, a second master suite with an en suite bathroom graces yet another wing of the house. Throughout, the home showcases your favorite modern touches, including quartz countertops, 42" cabinets, a 5-burner gas range, ceramic wood tile, a tankless water heater, and a pre-wired security system with Amazon™ Home Automation integration. Step into luxury both indoors and out, as the screened and pavered lanai beckons you to savor mornings and evenings in style. A sprinkler irrigation system tends to the grounds, creating a serene oasis. Located in the tranquil community of Madeira, you'll relish the peace and convenience, with downtown just 10 minutes away and beaches a mere 5 minutes further. Elevate your lifestyle with this meticulously designed residence – your haven awaits!
